== 媒體 ==
《赫特福德郡廣告報》（Herts Advertiser）是以聖奧爾本斯為基地的地區報章<ref>[http://www.britishpapers.co.uk/england-eang/herts-advertiser/ Herts Advertiser] {{Wayback|url=http://www.britishpapers.co.uk/england-eang/herts-advertiser/ |date=20201029144551 }}，britishpapers.co.uk。</ref>。其他地區報章有《聖奧爾本斯和哈彭登觀察家報》（St Albans & Harpenden Observer）和《聖奧爾本斯和哈彭登評論報》（St Albans & Harpenden Review）等，但其基地在聖奧爾本斯鄰近小鎮，而前者在2008年併入後者<ref>[http://www.britishpapers.co.uk/england-eang/st-albans-harpenden-review/ St Albans & Harpenden Review] {{Wayback|url=http://www.britishpapers.co.uk/england-eang/st-albans-harpenden-review/ |date=20101102012924 }}，britishpapers.co.uk。</ref><ref>[http://www.britishpapers.co.uk/england-eang/st-albans-observer/ St Albans & Harpenden Observer] {{Wayback|url=http://www.britishpapers.co.uk/england-eang/st-albans-observer/ |date=20201020023632 }}，britishpapers.co.uk。</ref>。

聖奧爾本斯位處[[英國廣播公司|英國廣播公司]]的[[BBC_East|東部地區]]（BBC East），地區電視新聞節目稱為《[[BBC_Look_East|BBC Look East]]》，於[[英國廣播公司第一台|英國廣播公司第一台]]播映；地區電台稱為《BBC三郡電台》（BBC Three Counties Radio）<ref>[http://www.bbc.co.uk/threecounties/content/articles/2009/03/17/rds_changes_feature_feature.shtml <!---Title--->BBC Three Counties on your RDS radio] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/threecounties/content/articles/2009/03/17/rds_changes_feature_feature.shtml |date=20130311080643 }}，BBC。網頁內「I listen to……」段落註明赫特福德郡（Herts）在收聽範圍，而聖奧爾本斯是郡內一鎮。</ref>。

